<p><a name="Notes" id="Notes"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Manifest_Destiny&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: Notes">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Notes</span></h2>
<div class="references-small references-column-count references-column-count-2" style="-moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;">
<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-0"><b><a href="#cite_ref-0" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=nCV7XjWY5nwC&amp;pg=PA218&amp;lpg=PA218&amp;dq=%22Nicholas+Guyatt%22+%22manifest+destiny%22&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=0OT8eG0j83&amp;sig=4EdsgvVMLhuioCEfaqF3MPH0-tQ&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=book_result&amp;resnum=1&amp;ct=result#PPA8,M1" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=nCV7XjWY5nwC&amp;pg=PA218&amp;lpg=PA218&amp;dq=%22Nicholas+Guyatt%22+%22manifest+destiny%22&amp;source=bl&amp;ots=0OT8eG0j83&amp;sig=4EdsgvVMLhuioCEfaqF3MPH0-tQ&amp;hl=en&amp;sa=X&amp;oi=book_result&amp;resnum=1&amp;ct=result#PPA8,M1" rel="nofollow">Nicholas Guyatt: <i>Providence and the Invention of the United States, 1607-1876</i></a><br />
